OL,9,FThe gender pay gap also varies between
OL,10,Fage groups and sectors.
OL,12,FThe information and communication
OL,13,Fsector saw the highest disparity at
OL,14,F28.2%, followed by financial and legal
OL,15,Factivities, and manufacturing.
OL,17,FMen are also paid more in age groups
OL,18,Fover 40 - with the highest gap of
OL,19,F16.1% recorded in the 55-59 group.
