OL,3,CJersey gender pay gap narrows but men
OL,4,Cstill earn 7.8% more
OL,6,FThe public sector's gender pay gap
OL,7,Fstands much higher than the overall
OL,8,Faverage at 19.7%.
OL,10,FDeputy Lindsay Feltham, Jersey's
OL,11,FSocial Security Minister, says that
OL,12,Fmore work needs to be done to narrow
OL,13,Fthe difference.
OL,15,FShe explains: "I think it's really
OL,16,Fimportant that the Government is a
OL,17,Fleader and as the largest employer on
OL,18,Fthe island, takes their gender pay gap
OL,19,Fseriously.
