OL,6,F"I've already asked my team to
OL,7,Fencourage employers to be more
OL,8,Ftransparent when they're advertising
OL,9,Ftheir roles."
OL,11,FIn 2023, the States of Guernsey said
OL,12,Fthey did not collect data that allowed
OL,13,Fthem to reliably report on the gender
OL,14,Fpay gap.
OL,16,FWhile they said there were plans to
OL,17,Fbegin reliable reporting in 2024, ITV
OL,18,FNews has not been able to find these
OL,19,Fresults.
